# CSS / SCSS

- Prefer design tokens or variables for colors, spacing, and typography when the project uses them.
- Avoid deep selector chains; prefer class-based styling consistent with the codebase.
- Use mobile-first or the project's responsive convention consistently.
- Avoid `!important` unless overriding third-party with documented reason.
- Co-locate styles with components when that is the project pattern.
